{
  "stem": "3928.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I did not know who executed the people, but I went through one time-- what was the name of the street?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE]-- no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE], I believe that was the name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When I seen, I would say, maybe four block-- blocks long people piled up like cardboard dead people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, I don't know if they were all Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I could not tell this, you know, really, because I did not do stop there and see it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Only I stopped for one time there, and I seen, and then somebody try-- people were looking for relatives, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was in-- in December.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- in-- in 1944-- and some of the bodies were frozen so much, you know, then when people tried to pick it up, just broke off.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and I seen this one, but who did the killing?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I could not tell, you know, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I know the people were there, you know, like piled up like cardboard, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's the way it were there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in-- in-- and in the ghetto itself, there wasn't too much of killing because they just robbed the people there-- you know, all their belongings.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, there was nothing unusual, you know, that people, you know, like the-- the-- the SS did not go into the ghettos.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a Hungarian Arrow Cross.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was nothing unusual to see somebody with a watch-- stop them, take the watch off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, or take a-- seen a good-looking woman, just took with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where they took them, I don't know, but took with them, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
